21 Mar 2015: Ebola breakthrough as test which spots victims BEFORE they fall ill will be available within a year
http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3006051/Ebola-breakthrough-test-spots-victims-fall-ill-available-year.html#ixzz3V9FVFqyh
[ProMED usually does not report new tests or vaccines until they are being field tested. It needs to be able to detect Lassa virus as well in this region, because the symptoms it causes are so similar to those of Ebola, and it is endemic there. - Mod.JW]

